                                        <li>
                                            <div class="media wow fadeInDown">
                                                <div class="media-body"><a class="catg_title"> Don't chose too many
                                                        differentials! Make sure to include some safe choices! </a>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <div class="media wow fadeInDown">
                                                <div class="media-body"><a class="catg_title"> Try not to Spend more
